lead_paragraph: Gareth Bale says Wales' Euro 2016 semi-final against Portugal on Wednesday will not be decided by his personal duel with Real Madrid team mate Cristiano Ronaldo.

headline.print_headline: Bale Plays Down Importance of Duel With Ronaldo at Euro 2016
headline.main: Bale Plays Down Importance of Duel With Ronaldo at Euro 2016
